{
  "stem": "10970.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Her name was Evelyn.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had a cafe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They ran the cafe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so they ran-- they-- and the house was their house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They lived right in-- behind the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she used to disappear-- the daughter used to disappear at night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She used to bring supplies-- because they had a cafe, they had access to food-- and she used to bring supplies to the French Free Forces.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were hiding in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, and then she would come back during-- in the morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I was aware of that, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She had told me, I believe she did, yeah, and told me to keep quiet.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never mentioned anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I recall they-- when I first came, they had to take me and register with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And unfortunately, I was not prompted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they asked me to give my name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I gave my name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, Raymonde Nathansohn.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was not supposed to.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was supposed to give their names.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And just by giving my name, I gave away that I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I saw their faces.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I could have killed us all at the same-- at that very time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the commandant said something to the effect that I looked like his daughter and let it go, and, I guess, let me stay there, but under their watchful eye.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I must have been maybe five, five or six at that point because I remember starting school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to walk 10 miles a day to go to school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The village-- was really a village-- was Raucourt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "R-A-U-C-O-U-R-T.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was several miles from Sedan in eastern-- in the Ardennes in France.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And where we-- the house was located was not even-- it was just a crossroads.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
